### Restaurant Management API Tests

### Get all restaurants
GET http://localhost:8000/api/restaurants

### Get restaurants with search
GET http://localhost:8000/api/restaurants?search=Tandoori

### Get restaurants with filters
GET http://localhost:8000/api/restaurants?cuisine=Japanese&location=Mumbai

### Get restaurants with sorting
GET http://localhost:8000/api/restaurants?sort_by=name&sort_order=desc

### Get specific restaurant
GET http://localhost:8000/api/restaurants/101

### Get order trends for restaurant
GET http://localhost:8000/api/restaurants/101/trends?start_date=2025-06-23&end_date=2025-06-30

### Get top restaurants by revenue
GET http://localhost:8000/api/analytics/top-restaurants?start_date=2025-06-23&end_date=2025-06-30

### Get filtered orders
GET http://localhost:8000/api/analytics/orders?restaurant_id=101&start_date=2025-06-23&end_date=2025-06-30

### Get orders with amount filter
GET http://localhost:8000/api/analytics/orders?min_amount=500&max_amount=1000

### Get orders with hour filter
GET http://localhost:8000/api/analytics/orders?start_hour=15&end_hour=18